{"tid":310270,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"2017-07-06 雲加又贏","createTime":"2017-07-05T16:10:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T16:25:23.000Z","uid":8883,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"528bbd70eb0ef7b3592afa88ddf06eea142ca228","tid":310270,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T16:10:02.000Z","msg":"簽入拿卡錫迪了，迷雲的勢力日漸浩大。很多人說，這不是我們熟悉的雲加。起初，雲加創造阿仙奴。球星是虛無的、是生產的，而不是簽。如今，雲加說要有拿卡，就有了拿卡。反雲開始慌了，是不是我又做錯了甚麼？去年，我哭著對你說，希古恩都是騙人的。你不可能，依賴那個來自德國的王子。今天，足總杯得到了，我們仿佛回到了那些年。山齊士、薩卡、哥拉辛拿斯，全是我們的！簽入多於三名球員是技術錯誤嘛？是！但我們就是要簽！把想簽的都簽過來！反雲哭了：「媽的！為何不是我想的那樣？這樣的雲加怎能反？！」有的按不住情緒，奔向迷雲。有的說要堅持反雲，卻私下出膿汁了。餘下的反雲所剩無幾，迷雲表示：「我們勝利了！」"},{"pid":"52bc3332425fe711acb21c8776740b523444975d","tid":310270,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T16:10:40.000Z","msg":"雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2452febb6ec888a2c3b8e3633a6d79a79d653477","tid":310270,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T16:11:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ad66a8c6c5c8bf984167dfd76842931505b2b0e2","tid":310270,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T16:11:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好想知反雲狗仲可以點吠"},{"pid":"53bbbc99d79dc2a75b2d78b7cfec53de2cbc9bd7","tid":310270,"uid":581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T16:11:33.000Z","msg":"永續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da8152117964053bcc766e4f6d9971b539dc875d","tid":310270,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T16:12:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>永續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果基本法同雲加只得一個可以永續 我會揀雲加"},{"pid":"6343f2860b0f9c90fc77990bb950cd17f34501da","tid":310270,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T16:13:27